        <li>Vacuum-adapted or reality-manipulating beings (weather is their plaything)</li>
        <li>Threats operating on Planck or geological time (patience of mountains)</li>
        <li>Completely invisible or extradimensional entities (stealth mode: maximum)</li>
        <li>Beings that treat physics as suggestions (house rules, cosmic edition)</li>
        <li>Hybrid entities combining multiple threat types (nightmare variety packs)</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
