#### Why 'Standard' Protocols Create Vulnerabilities

Here's the truly horrifying discovery that keeps our crisis management department in business: each defensive measure optimized for one threat type creates systematic vulnerabilities to others. It's not just that our defenses are inadequate‚Äîthey're counterproductive across the threat spectrum. It's like installing a burglar alarm that broadcasts your location to interdimensional thieves.

