### 2.2 Attack Mechanisms by Lethality Scale

The following analysis organizes alien elimination strategies by their scope and mechanism, from personal annihilation (just you, specifically) to universal extinction (everything, everywhere, everywhen). Each lethality category represents not just a different scale of damage, but fundamentally different approaches to the problem of eliminating opposition‚Äîdifferent answers to the question of how thoroughly your existence should be erased from the cosmic record. 

