    Asymmetric Vulnerability Matrix
  </h4>
  
  <p className="text-red-200 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
    This matrix demonstrates how each defensive strategy creates systematic vulnerabilities to alternative attack vectors. The mathematical result is that every defense type exhibits negative or marginal net effectiveness against multi-vector threats. It's like a comprehensive study of how to make things worse while trying to make them better. 
  </p>
  
