### Conclusion of Part 1

The evidence is overwhelmingly clear: contact equals catastrophe. The universe operates not merely with hostility, but with systematic efficiency in converting contact scenarios into extinction events. Conventional defense is not only useless but actively helpful to any entity that doesn't play by our rules. And no one plays by our rules.

